metadata.name: Under a Spell
metadata.description:
How nature can be so powerful and yet so beautiful at the same. Getting surrounded by something so powerful can affect your thoughts and feelings. By looking at this image, I felt like under a spell that I would never want to break.


Artist: Waheed Akhtar

Medium: Digital Art

Dimension: 4000 x 4000
